    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "FLY\nSOUTHWEST\nAIRLINES\nSeptember 8, 1989 Flight Schedule\nThe\nCompany\nPlane:\nis on call.\nNew Signals\nOf Success",
      "SOUTHWEST\nFLY\nAIRLINES\nPacific\nMountain\nCentral\nEastern\n(City \u0026 Metro)\nsan Francisc\nSan Diego\nNew Orleans\nPhoenix and Indianapolis do not observe\nDaylight Savings Time.\nSan Antonio,\n(Hobby \u0026 Intercontinental)\nCorpus\nChristi\nRio Grande Valley\n(Harlingen/South Padre Island)\nIf you fly frequently on Southwest Airlines,\nplease send us your name and address and we\nwill place you on our mailing list. Mail\nrequests to: Southwest Airlines Schedule List\nP.O. Box 650331\nDallas, TX 75265-0331\nAll other correspondence should be sent to:\nSouthwest Airlines Co.\nP.O. Box 37611\nDallas, TX 75235\n© 1989 Southwest Airlines"
    ],
